    <text x="40" y="100" fill="#7d7560" font-family="Charter, Cambria, Georgia, serif" font-style="italic" font-size="14">especially alone.</text>

    <text x="0" y="148" fill="#a13a28" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="0.18em">VII.</text>
    <text x="40" y="150" fill="#1f1c14" font-family="Charter, Cambria, Georgia, serif" font-size="20" font-weight="600">think in probabilities.</text>
    <text x="40" y="174" fill="#7d7560" font-family="Charter, Cambria, Georgia, serif" font-style="italic" font-size="14">never deal in absolutes.</text>

    <text x="0" y="222" fill="#a13a28" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" font-size="11" letter-spacing="0.18em">VIII.</text>
    <text x="40" y="224" fill="#1f1c14" font-family="Charter, Cambria, Georgia, serif" font-size="20" font-weight="600">leave leverage behind.</text>
